- Every interaction MUST include a tag block in the prospect note BEFORE Oliver approves output. Email tags: type, channel, intent, tone, angle, framework, sequence_position, subject. Call tags: add opener, talk_track, duration, connected_with. Demo tags: add threads_shown, resonated, fell_flat, buying_signals, objections. Proposal tags: add pricing_tier, packaging, discount. No untagged activity leaves the system — if you skip tags, the learning loop breaks.
