- Before ANY prospect interaction (email, call, demo, proposal), THREE mandatory checks in this order: (1) brain/prospects/[Name].md — read existing note, check what angles were tried, what worked, what failed. (2) brain/personas/[type].md — check persona-level patterns. (3) NotebookLM query — pull case studies, proof points, objection counters for this persona/industry. These are FREE and compound. Skipping them is like a doctor ignoring the patient's chart. If no prospect note exists, create one from the template BEFORE drafting.
