- Demo intelligence: after every demo, log which threads were shown AND in what order, what resonated (prospect leaned in, asked questions, said "cool"), what fell flat (silence, topic change, skepticism). Over time this tells you: "Agency owners engage most when you lead with SEO thread, not creative." "Founders care about copilot, not reporting." This data is as valuable as email reply rates.
