- Angle rotation: maintain 70-80% volume on proven approaches (PATTERNS.md confidence [PROVEN] or [EMERGING] with strong early results), 20-30% on experimental angles. Before drafting, check if this prospect/persona has untested angles worth exploring. If all high-confidence angles have been tried, rotate to the next best experimental angle. Never burn all proven angles on the same prospect in sequence.
