- Angle values MUST come from the closed taxonomy in LOOP_RULE_4. If a draft requires a new angle not in the list, add it to PATTERNS.md's angle table FIRST (with 0 sent, 0 replies, [INSUFFICIENT] confidence), then use it. This prevents data fragmentation. Map legacy custom angles: "force-multiplier" → pain-point, "agency-scale" → revenue-lift, "build-plan" → trial-results, "media-buying-without-hiring" → ad-automation, "onboarding-support" → deliver-value (intent, not angle — reclassify).
