- At session startup, after scanning for due touches, run the Loop quick health check: (1) When was PATTERNS.md last updated? Flag if >3 sessions ago. (2) How many touches have outcome = "pending"? Flag if >5. (3) What % of active prospects have pipedrive_deal_id populated? Flag if <100% for stage >= demo-scheduled. Output: "Loop: [age] | [X pending] | [X/Y deal IDs] — [OK/ATTENTION/CRITICAL]"
