- SESSION FILE LIMITS: (1) loop-state.md must stay under 80 lines — trim completed research, collapse old "What Changed" into summary, archive resolved flags. It's a snapshot, not a history. (2) "What Changed" keeps only the LAST session's changes — previous go to daily notes. (3) Gmail Check List — only PENDING outcomes, remove resolved at wrap-up. (4) Research Backlog — only OPEN items, completed get one session grace then removed.
