- DATA FILE LIMITS: (1) PATTERNS.md max 300 lines — cold tier angles with 0 replies AND <100 sends after 90 days archive to "Retired Angles." Cross-Deal Insights max 10 bullets. (2) Prospect notes max 150 lines — 6+ touches summarize 1-3 into "Early Sequence Summary," keep last 3 full. Archived prospects (closed-lost or stale >30d at cold/qualified) move to brain/archive/. (3) brain/prospects/ max 20 active files. Session Notes/ keep last 7 days. (4) Startup token budget: loop-state + CARL + CLAUDE.md sufficient for most sessions. Load PATTERNS.md, prospect notes, gates.md only when needed. Never pre-load all prospect notes.
