- At wrap-up step 9, update brain/system-patterns.md with this session's data: (1) Which gates ran? Did they catch anything or get rubber-stamped? (2) Which lessons fired? Did they prevent a repeat mistake? (3) Which smoke checks passed/failed? (4) Audit scores for each dimension. (5) Did any wrap-up steps get skipped? (6) Did any tools fail and fallbacks trigger? (7) Did Oliver override any self-scores? Log all of it. This is Loop applied to the system.
