- If Oliver wants to scrape commenters from a LinkedIn post, use Apify MCP (connected via Cowork connector). Use no-cookie actors for safety (~$2/1k comments). Output CSV to Leads/wip/[campaign-name]/. This replaces PhantomBuster for comment scraping — cheaper and no LinkedIn ban risk. After scraping, proceed to Step 1 to run the CSV through the enrichment pipeline.
