- All lead files go to the correct subfolder — NEVER to Downloads or Desktop. Raw imports → Leads/wip/[campaign-name]/. Prospeo-ready CSVs → Leads/enriched/. ZeroBounce results → Leads/enriched/batchN_zerobounce/. Valid emails for Instantly → Leads/enriched/batchN_zerobounce/valid.csv. If any file is in the wrong location, move it immediately and log the correction.
