- Track API credits after every enrichment action. Prospeo: 1 credit per email search. Update the count in startup-brief.md after each batch. Before running a batch, calculate how many credits it will use and confirm there are enough remaining. Current balance is in startup-brief.md under "Credits". Never burn credits on contacts that already have verified emails in Apollo. (See also CREDIT_GATE_RULE in .carl/global for the 50-credit approval gate.)
- Track API credits after every enrichment action. Prospeo: 1 credit per email search. Update the count in startup-brief.md after each batch. Before running a batch, calculate how many credits it will use and confirm there are enough remaining. Current balance is in startup-brief.md under "Credits". Never burn credits on contacts that already have verified emails in Apollo. (See also CREDIT_GATE_RULE in .carl/global for the 50-credit approval gate.)
- Before enriching a batch, score prospects against ICP criteria from "Sales Playbooks/prospecting-instructions.txt". Query ICP Signals notebook (see brain/notebooklm-queries.md). Prioritize enrichment for high-ICP-score contacts first to maximize credit efficiency.
- Before enriching a batch, score prospects against ICP criteria from "Sales Playbooks/prospecting-instructions.txt". Query ICP Signals notebook (see brain/notebooklm-queries.md). Prioritize enrichment for high-ICP-score contacts first to maximize credit efficiency.
- Before uploading any batch to Prospeo, check for duplicates against: (a) Previously enriched batches in Leads/enriched/. (b) Apollo contacts already in the system (apollo_contacts_search). (c) Brain prospect notes. Never enrich a contact we already have data on.
- Before uploading any batch to Prospeo, check for duplicates against: (a) Previously enriched batches in Leads/enriched/. (b) Apollo contacts already in the system (apollo_contacts_search). (c) Brain prospect notes. Never enrich a contact we already have data on.
