- When Google Sheets is available (Rube MCP connected), use it as the live tracking layer: (a) Apify scrape output goes directly into a campaign Sheet instead of just a local CSV. (b) Each campaign gets one Sheet with tabs: Raw Commenters | ICP Scored | Enriched | Verified | Sent | Replied. (c) Update enrichment status per row as leads move through the pipeline. (d) Track credit usage in a Credits tab. This replaces CSV-juggling with a single live view Oliver can check from his phone.
